# GitHub Workflow Rules (CouncilWorks)

## Issue Management

- Migrate TODOs to issues with clear acceptance criteria
- Use labels: enhancement, bug, documentation, security, database, auth
- Provide effort estimates and link related PRs

## Branch Strategy and Standards

- **main**: Production-ready, stable code only
- **develop**: Integration branch for ongoing development
- **feature/***: Individual feature development branches from develop

Naming:
- Feature: `feature/issue-123-short-description`
- Fix: `fix/issue-123-short-description`
- Docs: `docs/topic-name`
- Refactor: `refactor/component-name`

## PR Template

```markdown
## Related Issue
Fixes #[issue_number]

## Changes
- [Change 1]

## Testing
- [ ] Unit tests
- [ ] Integration tests

## Checklist
- [ ] Code follows style guidelines
- [ ] Tests added/updated
- [ ] Documentation updated
```

## Commit Standards

```
type(scope): description
```

Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, test, chore

